个尾喷口。而歼-35A是双发动机战机，有2个尾喷口。 这家美国权威军事媒体还不无揶揄地写道：“考虑到该办公室的责任是确保美军的F-35战机时刻待命，我们原以为他们的工作人员会非常熟悉这款战机的细节，可目前看来，事实并非如此。” 一些比较“毒舌”的美国网民也没有放过这个机会，其中一个美国网民指出：这个海报的右下角就有一个F-35标志，难道工作人员没想着对比一下吗？（环球时报新媒体）"},"attached_info":"CkEI/KmF85Kt3ZBNEAMaCTExMTc4OTUzOCDs8NG5BjAAOJgBQAFyCjQwNjQ2MTcyNzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"195 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-123966fd8b1a024096c67cfa1e505b57_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1731835167.457193","card_id":"Q_596279235","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":596279235,"title":"老北京话“沏壶高的”是什么意思？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/596279235","type":"question","created":1681795950,"answer_count":142,"follower_count":202,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[491,1089,7598,34938,182301],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I/KmF85Kt3ZBNEAMaCDk0Nzg3NjcwIO7W+KEGMAA4ygFAAnIJNTk2Mjc5MjM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"177 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7f44f725537988930126eff5a497b3ff_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1731835167.457515","card_id":"Q_31630184","target":{"id":31630184,"title":"如何建构一个完整的故事框架?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/31630184","type":"question","created":1435250723,"answer_count":21,"follower_count":798,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[767,21767,42364],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerp